    "To what extent does GenAI-enhanced knowledge management impact the overall productivity and innovation of an organization?",
    "What are the best approaches to training knowledge workers to effectively apply GenAI in support of their activities?",
    "How should knowledge work and knowledge flows be redesigned to harness GenAI capabilities?",
    "Which domains and use cases benefit from the integration of GenAI and in which areas might its use be counterproductive?",
    "The focus on IT's contribution to knowledge management (Alavi & Leidner, 2001; Alavi & Denford, 2011) has paved the way for research and exploration in this domain."
